      "overview": "<p><strong>OVERVIEW</strong></p><p><br></p><p>The deck relies on [[Standing Stones]] to make Pith Imps Spellcasters, and to make tokens spellcaster and end with a massive Occult Rotual into Arcane Barrage. </p><p><br></p><p>Other ways of winning are Powerwish to make you enormousnand then attack through a Sphere of Animosity. Some other ten cool interactions like Rule + Plague are in.</p><p><br></p>"
