    "guide": {
      "overview": "<p><a href=\"https://youtu.be/v-1IyJiJvz0\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/v-1IyJiJvz0</a></p><p><br></p><p>Quite a strong token based deck, making lots of skeletons and then using mass pumps/lords to get huge value.</p><p><br></p><p>Try to use your avatar ability every turn, a great turn 2 is just spending 1 mana to make a skeleton with your avatar ability and 1 mana to make a skeleton with an open grave/mausoleum.</p><p><br></p><p>Has a bit of a Spellcaster subtheme for Vivien. She is amazing in this deck. Getting double your avatar ability is great, and she can copy Novice Necromancer, Master Necromancer and Grandmaster Wizard.</p><p><br></p><p>potential:</p><p>entombed (big but doesnt fit token strat)</p><p>witching hour (1 mana more and you get permanent lord buffs)</p><p><br></p><p>reanimator package?</p><p>carrionette</p><p>draconian bonekite</p><p>army of the dead</p>"
    },
