    "guide": {
      "overview": "<p>Forever engrailed Heirto the Realm,</p><p>Men of Kings loyal fraught thou beasts,</p><p>Though Opus magnum forgotten without,</p><p>One root Unbroken foretell Disaster,</p><p>Intruid Divinations coffers up Suffice Sacrifice,</p><p>Two Worlds on the Paths of War,</p><p>Perished Above the Darkness,</p><p>The Day of Judgement unfolds,</p><p>Triumphs of Light Through Desolation,</p><p>Wanderer of wonders and Devils Despite,</p><p>Angel and Demon Sounds bound by souls,</p><p>Sorcery contented for Divine Destiny.</p><h2><strong><u>Pfadfinder eine unerzählte Legende.</u></strong></h2>"
    },
