    "guide": {
      "overview": "<p>Max Skeleton start:</p><p><br></p><p>Turn 1 play Boulevard of Bones. Summon 1 skeleton.</p><p><br></p><p>Turn 2 play Open Grave/Mausoleum forward. Summon 3 skeletons.</p><p><br></p><p>Turn 3 play Mirror Realm right of Boulevard copying it and cast Novice Necromancer. Summon 3 skeletons.</p><p>You can Panpipes turn 3 for 6 damage and try to force opponet to Dispel/Disenchant to protect your +1 buffs turn 4+.</p><p><br></p><p>Turn 4 if no +1 buff play Forsaken Crypt right of Mirror Realm. Summon 2 skeletons.</p><p><br></p><p>Turn 5 play Den of Evil forward of Mirror Realm and cast Returned King. Summon 2 skeletons.</p><p>Or play non-Open Grave/Masoleum/Forsaken Crypt forward of Mirror Realm, cast Landmass, and play Open Grave/Mausoleum. Summon 3 skeletons.</p><p><br></p><p>Turn 6 don't play site left of Boulevard and cast Master Necromancer. Summon 5 skeletons.</p><p>Or play Open Grave/Masoleum left of Boulevard and cast 2x Novice Necromancer. Summon 5 skeletons.</p><p><br></p><p>End of turn 6: 17x skeletons</p><p>--------</p><p>Use Bone Spear for game win. Spore Spouts/Tactical Move/Landmass will help position a skeleton for the projectile.</p><p><br></p><p>Pile of Skulls can banish from the enemy cemetery, do this to save your cemetery for Book of the Dead.</p>"
    },
