    "guide": {
      "overview": "<h2><strong>Deck Overview</strong></h2><p>Drop a big minion in the cemetery and using Raise Dead or Boneyard to bring it back into the game.</p><p><br></p><h2><strong>Card Choices</strong></h2><p>Seer, Browse, Dream Quest, Observatory, and Rivers can help filter through your deck to find the key cards you need to pull this off.</p><p><br></p><p>The non-big minions are all draw or tutor minions.</p><p><br></p><p>An early well placed Wizard's Den can trick opponent into attacking it allowing you to discard a large minion to reanimate the next turn.</p><p><br></p><p>Defensive spells, auras, and sites to stay alive until you can get some large minions on the board.</p>"
    },
