    "guide": {
      "overview": "<p>Check out my video deck tech for Ironclad here! https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5GIB4AyE2kw</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>Using Ironclads ability to reduce the cost on self-damaging spells Searing Truth and Pnakotic Manuscript for very efficient card draw. Sugarplum Pixies untaps us at the end of turn and we can use our Avatar to block attacks and reduce damage taken (My Body As A Shield) The Inquisitions free summon trigger applies when revealing through our card draw spells and that is a really powerful tempo swing!</p><p>We have a lock on strike damage with Golden Harp allowing us to order the modifiers in a way that we take no damage from strikes. The Poisonous Dagger lets us kill anything when we block.</p>"
    },
