    "guide": {
      "overview": "<p>Main idea</p><p><br></p><p>only play 2-3 sites, after that only play a site if you have overflow. This allows us to play a site and still attack (which may make it water better just for this reason)</p><p><br></p><p>use cards to disable minions, I’m going water for this deck because frost nova compared to poison nova is 1 less mana and I want to burst people as fast as possible with Bladedancers ability.</p><p><br></p><p>overpower and invigorate are pretty nuts, if used correctly over power can cause 6 damage with blade dancers ability.</p><p><br></p><p>this a just framework will make changes accordingly</p><p><br></p><p>Played a few games decks has hella burst and “The Rack” is nuts becuase you can attack avatars directly twice! Which would do and extra 5 damage with your first two hits</p><p><br></p><p>I got most people down to deaths door if I lost so I added Ice Lance (idk why I didn’t have it earlier) probably the most fun I had with an avatar</p><p><br></p><p>tweaking a few things, sphere of animosity, avatars such as interrogator/battlemage hard counter us. Keeping this in mind Voltron style decks seem kinda weak and very inconsistent, my other deck dancer of the pale worm may be a more consistent deck than this one, however this deck is definitely fun! </p>"
    },
