    "guide": {
      "overview": "<p>Full Primer coming soon! Never mind. While I do feel like this deck has potential if tuned properly, it is so boring to play with and against that I'd rather not be the one to tune it. </p><p><br></p><p>The general idea here is to test if Witch can operate with only 1-3 super defensible sites and then just sit there - untouchable - and drain the opponent for 2 until they're at Death's Door. Then, just drop a site for threshold and finish them off with a spell. If this deck ends up being good it's going to be miserable to play against. I'm sorry, everyone.</p>"
    },
